media: imx: imx7-mipi-csis: Fix MEDIA_BUS_FMT_UYVY8_2X8 data alignment

The MEDIA_BUS_FMT_UYVY8_2X8 format reports a data alignment of 16 bits,
which isn't correct as it is output on an 8-bit bus. Fix it.

